data.description: Opportunity awaits! Multi-generational split level home in a quiet country setting only a few miles to amenities. TWO COMPLETE LIVING SPACES to meet your needs. Breath in the fresh air and enjoy the spectacular panoramic views. Stay cozy & warm with 2 fireplaces plus a free standing wood stove in addition to the forced air with a/c. Upstairs you will find a living room, dining room, kitchen, primary suite complete with a 3/4 bathroom as well as two more bedrooms, a bathroom & a utility room. Downstairs includes a family room, kitchen, bedroom, bathroom & bonus room as well as access to the attached garage. Nearly 6 acres with 2.5 of them on irrigation, a detached shop, 2 apple trees, 2 walnut trees, grapes & pasture leaves room to roam.
